chat.msg: hey there, estas listo?
hey, si estoy listo.
well, looks like we're at the start
to my left there's a twig leading to a little island with a tiger. where should i go?
You should go between the tiger and the twig but below the rock.
alright, i see an island with a butterfly to my right and a big island with a parrot on my left
which way to go, mate?
You should go to the island with the parrot near the trees.
got it, now i'm standing with the parrot
next?
Walk around the tree counterclockwise, but do not pass the elephant. Once you see a rock path, pass it to get the island with the frog
cool, i'm now on the island with the frog and a crocodile
where to now?
Walk toward the frog a bit and do a u-turn to towards the crocodile and cross it.
crossed the crocodile safely, and hey, there's that elephant again
what's next?
Ignore the elephant, walk towards the island with the giraffe using the rock path.
alright, now i'm standing next to the giraffe and a snake is to my right
where to next?
Walk towards the island with the snake.
ok, took a step to the snake
what's my next move?
Walk towards the island with the snake and continue walking futher into the island.
took a couple of steps further and guess what? bingo! there's the treasure *finished*
hola, q tal? ready to play?
Yes, I am ready to play
great! see the white dog? head left a bit, under the bench. right across that trail, you're heading for the florist stand, but don't get there yet
surprise twist – we're u-turning it! cross the trail again and head right back to mr. white dog. how's it going so far?
Going good
awesome! now, cross over the bench to the south and keep going that way. you'll spot another white dog
he's hosting a picnic with a lovely red and white checkered blanket. keep going!
Done
good job! see that mat over there? walk right over it till you touch that bowl of berries, then head west
There
well done! now head north over that wooden branch crossing the river
feeling like an adventurer yet?
Yes, definitely
cool! now, you'll notice a green bush
don't touch it, but instead circle it from the right until you reach the florist stand
Done
awesome! now, make a left and head under the stand until you reach a big ol' bridge with two people cycling
head west and pass that bridge
Done
good stuff! just past the bridge, there's a couple of elders on a bench deep in their reading- got it?
Got it
lovely! now, head south, between the old folks and another branch
you'll find a green bush by the end of the branch
What is next?
from there, head east between the branch and the bush
not far now!
What else?
few steps east and say hello to a young brown deer
you made it! great job! how do you feel?
hola, you ready?
Yes, I am ready
sweet! i'm by the tent up north
where do we head next mate?
Go down and stay east of the two bushes.
alright! heading down east of the bushes
i see a dog and a fire, where to next?
Walk between the dog and fire but stay under the bush next to the fire
gotcha! going between the dog and the fire, staying under the bush
Now head over to the car but stay under the mushrooms
on it, heading to the car under the mushrooms
what next?
Do a u-turn on the path and start heading south of the trail
roger that, doing a u-turn and heading down south on the trail
Do you see a telescope?
yep, i see a blue telescope, should i proceed that way?
Yes
okay! heading to the telescope! what's the next step?
Go between the telescope and the bush on the path
doing so, going between the telescope and the bush on the path
what's next?
Follow the trail a little further
okay, done
now, what's next?
Do you see the cabin?
yep, i see it! woodland cabin, right?
Yes, go towards the woodland cabin
got it! heading towards the woodland cabin
*finished*! good job with the directions!
hey, estas listo?
si, estoy listo
genial, partamos. baja un poco hacia el suroeste debajo de la primera palmera, luego gira a la derecha y cruza la segunda palmera
¿ves la tercera palmera? gira bruscamente a la izquierda antes de llegar a ella. sigue hacia el sur
Que mas
ahora, vas a ver un cachorrito marrón
lo pasas por la izquierda y tomas un ligero giro a la izquierda, y luego a la derecha hacia el sur. ¿listo?
Donde
veras un par de rocas, una grande a la izquierda y otra pequeña a la derecha
pasa justo en medio de ellas y llegarás al agua
Liso
perfecto
entra al agua. ¿ves el gran cangrejo rojo? gira a la derecha, o sea, hacia el oeste y toma el camino largo de la roca grande
Cual roca grande
esa que tienes justo a la derecha. sigue hacia el oeste en el agua
enseguida te encuentras con una roca mediana. ¿la ves?
Si
genial, al encontrarte con el tiburón en el agua, gira bruscamente a la derecha
Donde exactamente
sal del agua y pisa tierra firme de nuevo. vas a cruzar entre la roca mediana y una pelota tricolor: azul, amarillo y blanco
sigue hacia el norte. ¿lo tienes?
Si
ahora, toma un ligero giro a la izquierda y sigue hacia el noroeste, entre esa carpa roja a tu izquierda y el altavoz grande a tu derecha
Liso
excelente, ahora da la vuelta a la carpa en un recorrido curvo y luego dirígete hacia el sur hacia el mar
Que mas
cuando llegues a la orilla, gira a la derecha
verás un kayak rojo? bien, ve por debajo de él
Aqui estoy
perfecto, da un giro de 90 grados a la derecha, o sea al norte, junto al kayak
Que mas
sigue ese camino hasta que llegues a un pequeño arbusto verde
